97
00:04:51,671 --> 00:04:52,871
Fais-moi l'amour.

98
00:04:54,330 --> 00:04:55,582
Non, je peux pas.

99
00:04:57,207 --> 00:04:58,793
Tu me trouves pas attirante ?

100
00:04:59,053 --> 00:04:59,866
Si.

